            <h1>Flash dance parties</h1>
            
            <p class="subtitle-paragraph margin-top-20 margin-bottom-50 clear-fix">
              Starting in the spring we will be hosting flash dance parties once a month at different locations all around San Francisco. 
              <span class="bold">We will announce the show 24 hours in advance and text you the location a few hours before the party starts. Parties will start at 1am and go til the sunrise.</span>
            </p>

             <%= form_for @rager do |f| %>
              <%= f.text_field :email, :placeholder => "Email", :style => "height:25px;" %>
              <%= f.submit "Request an invite", :style => "color:white;background-color:black;height:30px;width:150px;font-size:120%;" %>
            <% end %>

          </li>
