                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <span>2</span>
                          <h5>Tell us about yourself</h5>
                          <p>Once you request an invite we will send you a little survey with a few fun and simple questions to fill out so we can get to know you a little better.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <span>3</span>
                          <h5>Once your invited</h5>
                          <p>Any person who is invited will need to share with us their phone number so we can text you the location of the event and password to get in.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <span>4</span>
                          <h5>Dance all night long</h5>
                          <p>The sole focus of our dance parties will be music, fun, and dancing! Make sure to bring a smile.</p>
                        </li>

